@jaogarcia97 I don’t think the issue is run_demo_loop itself. `__fake_id__` is injected when the SDK is calling a non-OpenAI Responses API.

This error typically occurs when mixing models from different providers and then sending non-OpenAI chat history to the OpenAI Responses API.

Could you confirm which OpenAI Agents SDK version you’re using? Please try upgrading to the latest v0.6.5, which improves cross-model compatibility and may already resolve this issue.
